{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "embolsadora-api-master-collection",
    "name": "Embolsadora API - Complete Collection",
    "description": "Master collection for Embolsadora 4.0 Cloud API\n\nConsolidated endpoints across all features:\n- Auth (Supabase JWT)\n- Invitations CRUD\n- Tenants management\n- Users CRUD\n- User Role Assignments\n- Edge Device Management (Complete US1-US9)\n\n**Base URL:** `{{baseUrl}}` = http://localhost:8080\n\n**Authentication:** Bearer JWT Token (usar POST Login para obtenerlo)\n**Multi-tenant:** `X-Tenant-ID: {{tenant_uuid}}` header requerido en la mayoría de endpoints\n\n**Auth Endpoints (002-supabase-auth-backend):**\n- POST /api/v1/auth/login\n- GET /api/v1/me\n- POST /api/v1/auth/change-password\n\n**Invitation Endpoints:**\n- GET /api/v1/invitations\n- POST /api/v1/invitations\n- POST /api/v1/invitations/:id/resend\n- DELETE /api/v1/invitations/:id\n\n**Edge Device Endpoints (All 9 User Stories Implemented):**\n- US1: List Devices - GET /api/tenants/:tenantId/edge-devices\n- US2: Create Device - POST /api/tenants/:tenantId/edge-devices\n- US3: Get Device - GET /api/tenants/:tenantId/edge-devices/:deviceId\n- US4: Update Device - PUT /api/tenants/:tenantId/edge-devices/:deviceId\n- US5: Enable/Disable - POST /api/tenants/:tenantId/edge-devices/:deviceId/enable, /disable\n- US6: Status Check - POST /api/tenants/:tenantId/edge-devices/:deviceId/status\n- US7: Health Check - POST /api/tenants/:tenantId/edge-devices/:deviceId/health-check\n- US8: Telemetry - GET /api/tenants/:tenantId/edge-devices/:deviceId/telemetry\n- US9: Events - GET /api/tenants/:tenantId/edge-devices/:deviceId/events",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.access_token) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token', res.access_token);",
                  "  console.log('Token guardado en variable token');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Test1234!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login con email y contraseña. Guarda automáticamente el access_token en la variable de entorno `token`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Retorna el perfil del usuario autenticado (user, tenant, role, permissions). No requiere X-Tenant-ID."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Me (con tenant)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"},
              {"key": "X-Tenant-ID", "value": "{{tenant_uuid}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Retorna el perfil completo incluyendo tenant, rol y permisos."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Change Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/change-password",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "change-password"]
            },
            "description": "Limpia el flag password_change_required. Llamar desde el frontend después de que el usuario completó el cambio de contraseña en Supabase. No requiere X-Tenant-ID."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Invitations",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET List Invitations",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"},
              {"key": "X-Tenant-ID", "value": "{{tenant_uuid}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/invitations",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "invitations"]
            },
            "description": "Lista todas las invitaciones del tenant. Filtrar por status: ?status=pending|accepted|revoked|expired"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET List Invitations (filtro pending)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"},
              {"key": "X-Tenant-ID", "value": "{{tenant_uuid}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/invitations?status=pending",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "invitations"],
              "query": [{"key": "status", "value": "pending"}]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Create Invitation",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"},
              {"key": "X-Tenant-ID", "value": "{{tenant_uuid}}"},
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"nuevo@test.com\",\n  \"role_id\": \"operario\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/invitations",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "invitations"]
            },
            "description": "Crea una invitación y envía el email via Supabase. Requiere permiso invitations:write (rol admin o cliente_admin). Responde 409 si ya hay una invitación pendiente para ese email."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Resend Invitation",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"},
              {"key": "X-Tenant-ID", "value": "{{tenant_uuid}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/invitations/{{invitation_id}}/resend",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "invitations", "{{invitation_id}}", "resend"]
            },
            "description": "Reenvía el email de invitación. La invitación debe estar en estado pending. Requiere permiso invitations:write."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "DELETE Revoke Invitation",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"},
              {"key": "X-Tenant-ID", "value": "{{tenant_uuid}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/invitations/{{invitation_id}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "invitations", "{{invitation_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Revoca una invitación (cambia estado a revoked). Requiere permiso invitations:write."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Users (Auth)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST Force Password Change",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"},
              {"key": "X-Tenant-ID", "value": "{{tenant_uuid}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{user_id}}/force-password-change",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "users", "{{user_id}}", "force-password-change"]
            },
            "description": "Fuerza el cambio de contraseña de un usuario: activa el flag password_change_required y envía email de reset via Supabase. El usuario target debe pertenecer al tenant activo. Requiere permiso users:write."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
